title: Eminem - The Shady Shizzle Uncensored Collection (iTunes M4A)
description:
Cover: http://bayimg.com/daaMOAAGa

This was a neglected project that ran from 2011 to 2013 which has come back to life late 2014. Please seed, Sharing is Caring.

While most of this was mastered to sound completely perfect, some songs were edited to fill in the censored lyrics, so don't complain about a few of the songs not sounding right.

Synopsis:
Eminem has been a controversial figure since he first became big in the rap industry. Touching many taboo and difficult topics, offending many people of different views, religions, etc... Due to this, many of his lyrics were censored, even on the explicit version of the album.

Then there were rumors of a "secret" album called "The Shady Shizzle Collection", that was supposed to have all of these lyrics uncensored. Until today (August 27th, 2014) that was a rumor. Since no one else had it or tried to "create" it, me and two other people decided to do it together and give it to you for free.
